Updates from Alpha:
  1. Reward system added
    - Point system added for completing tasks
    - Point tracker added
    - Screen changes colour with rank (bronze, silver, gold) which is based on points from completed
      tasks - more ranks and rewards to be added in the future.
  2. Time/Date system
    - Once the time/date is set, if the task is not completed within that time/date, the task is failed and you get no points
    - Pop-up added for incorrect time/dates
  3. Task history
    - Can now see if a task is completed/failed in the task history screen
  4. Tests added
    - Started doing unit/instrumented tests
    - Setup codecov
    - Setup codacy
